											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The player awakes to find Lae'zel is on top of SH, a dagger pressed to her throat/chest (whichever works better). The rest of the scene plays out with Lae'zel over a prone Shadowheart, unless SH manages to get to her feet before combat (which will be noted in the specific nodes).&#xD;&#xA;" />
