											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Lae'zel rushes Shadowheart, stabbing her below the ribcage, Shadowheat falls to the ground. Leaving her to bleed out (1HP), Lae'zel takes the artefact and moves to leave. As she does so...&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;The artefact appears to vibrate in her hands. Lae'zel has just enough time to cock her head and look at the item quizically before a blast of pisonic energy overcomes her. In a wider angle, the psionic explosion engulfs her. Shadowheart, still on the ground, is splattered with Lae'zel's blood." />
										</node>
									</children>
								</node>
							</children>
						</node>
